column5: Does anyone know what happened to "Trailer Guy' always one of my favorite posters and always had great insight. I miss his thoughts and was wondering what may have happened to him.

Trailerguy Trailerguy is offline Wallhanger Send Message User Lists User Notes (1)Edit User ProfileLast Activity: 11-04-2008 10:10 PM He hasn't been on this site under that name for over 5 years. Sorry, I don't have a clue what happened to him.
I miss that guy, he always had the inside scoop on Wabby. Glad to see BigMike is back.
Thanks, I hope is getting his wish......."wishin I was fishin Wabby"
